# VibeMarketer — UI Redesign (Zed.dev-inspired)

## Design Philosophy

Redesigned the entire UI to follow Zed.dev's aesthetic: **clean, minimal, and powerful**. Removed all glassmorphism, gradients, and glow effects in favor of flat surfaces, subtle borders, generous whitespace, and muted colors.

## Before → After

| Element | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| Background | Deep navy + gradient sidebar | Soft charcoal `#1e2030` everywhere |
| Borders | Glowing, multi-layered | 1px, nearly invisible `7% white` |
| Buttons | Purple gradient + glow shadow | Flat solid `#7c8aff`, no shadow |
| Cards | Glassmorphism `rgba()` overlays | Simple 1px border containers |
| Typography | 14px with gradient text | 13px base, clean hierarchy |
| Sidebar | Heavy chrome | Minimal, same background as main |
| Colors | Vibrant purple, saturated | Muted blue-grey, desaturated accents |

