## Changes Made

- Rewrote [index.css](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/vibemarketer/src/index.css) — 953 lines → 620 lines (35% smaller)
- Removed all `var(--gradient-*)`, `var(--shadow-glow)`, `var(--bg-glass*)`
- New muted palette: `--accent: #7c8aff`, `--bg-base: #1e2030`
- Generous `--space-xl: 40px`, `--space-2xl: 64px` for content padding
- Sidebar narrowed to 240px with same-bg blending
- All verified working at `http://localhost:5173/`
